title: Yuumi teleports to enemy turret
body: I was playing Yuumi when I suddenly teleported to the enemy mid turret and almost died. I don't know how this happened but my guess is that I tried jumping to Poppy but the moment I did that Twisted Fate teleported with his ult

replies.body:
everything is working fine
- Rito Games 2019
I saw a post with the same kind of thing happening on the boards like a week ago
